reviews.review_text: A VERY nice aud... ...of one of the best (imho) played shows of '89.  Certainly top 2 or 3 of that summer.  Such sweet memories!  I rarely give 5, but after hearing that Iko again, I just can't give less.

bass this fob has more bottom end that the clugston remaster but maybe not as much midrange punch.  the levels are set a tad low as well.

probable prefer the other but they are both very good


this is my preffered copy
http://www.archive.org/details/gd1989-07-07.fob.clugston.10925.sbeok.shnf
